name: Soil loss (tonnes per hectare - scaled) [grid] - Existing land cover
description: This map depicts the average annual soil loss in metric tonnes per hectare*10e4 under the existing land use/land cover scenario for 2011.

name: Soil loss (tonnes per hectare - scaled) [grid] - Natural vegetation removed
description: This map depicts the average annual soil loss in metric tonnes per hectare*10e4 under a land use/land cover scenario in which natural vegetation has been replaced with barren land for 2011.

name: Sediment yield (tonnes per hectare - scaled) [grid] - Existing land cover
description: This map depicts the average annual sediment yield to waterbodies in metric tonnes per hectare*10e4 under the existing land use/land cover scenario for 2011.

name: Sediment yield (tonnes per hectare - scaled) [grid] - Natural vegetation removed
description: This map depicts the average annual sediment yield to the nearest waterbody in metric tonnes per hectare*10e4 under a land use/land cover scenario in which natural vegetation has been replaced with barren land for 2011.
